@startuml
skinparam linetype ortho
actor User
participant "Bot Handlers" as Bot
participant "FastAPI /bot/*" as API
participant "SQLite DB" as DB

User -> Bot: /start
Bot -> API: POST /bot/users/sync\n{telegram_id, username}
API -> DB: INSERT/UPDATE User
API --> Bot: UserDTO
Bot --> User: Главное меню

User -> Bot: 📚 Выбрать категорию
Bot -> API: GET /bot/categories
API -> DB: SELECT * FROM Category
API --> Bot: list[CategoryDTO]
Bot --> User: Список категорий

User -> Bot: Выбор категории (callback)
Bot -> API: GET /bot/categories/{id}/lessons
API -> DB: SELECT * FROM Lesson WHERE category_id=?
API --> Bot: list[LessonDTO]
Bot -> API: GET /bot/users/{tg_id}/progress/{cat_id}
API -> DB: SELECT lesson_id FROM UserProgress\nWHERE learned=TRUE
API --> Bot: {completed_lessons: [...]}
Bot --> User: Список уроков (с ✅/📄)

User -> Bot: Выбор урока (callback)
Bot -> API: GET /bot/lessons/{id}
API -> DB: SELECT * FROM Lesson
API --> Bot: LessonDTO (title, content)
Bot --> User: Текст урока + клавиатура действий
@enduml